      <div xml:id="Aink2">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> vāḻi yātaṉ vāḻi yaviṉi</l>
          <l> viḷaika vayalē varuka viravala</l>
          <l> reṉavēṭ ṭōḷē yāyē yāmē</l>
          <l> pallitaḻ nīlamoṭu neyta ṉikarkkun</l>
          <l> taṇṭuṟai yūraṉ kēṇmai </l>
          <l> vaḻivaḻic ciṟakka veṉavēṭ ṭēmē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> 'May you live long, Ātaṉ! May you live long, Aviṉi!</l>
          <l> May the paddy fields ripen! May the beggars come!' </l>
          <l> That's what our mother wants. As for us: </l>
          <l> 'The bond [I have] with the man from the village by the cool ghat</l>
          <l> where waterlilies rival many-petalled lotuses —</l>
          <l> may it grow step by step!' — that's what we want. </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
